      <hedline>
        <hl1>Estate of the Nation</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Christopher Stansfield letter on Nelson W Aldrich Jr's September 3 article on estate tax holds neither heirs nor goverment deserve parents' wealth (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Do heirs deserve their parents' wealth? Probably not, but neither does the government. The proper question is whether people deserve to see their property go where they want it to go, or whether they should see it seized by others. In a fair society, there is only one answer to that question.</p>
        <p>Christopher Stansfield  New York</p>
      </block>
